Outline - Hangman Game

Press any key to get started

Word array[] - Holds all words for the game

* Word Display
  -Display each letter (word.length) on screen with underline for each char.
  -Reveal letter when user selects

*Record the number of guesses remaining

*Wins: (# of times the user has guessed the letter correctly)

*Losses: (# of times the user has failed to guess the letter correctly after exhausting all guesses)

*Letter display area for incorrect letters guessed
  - # of guesses are not lowered when the same letter has been guessed

* when user wins, display a "correct!" word or image

*After win select another word

*After loss, reset game

*Style game

*play a sound when the "correct!" word/image is displayed *BONUS*
